{"tid":1125081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［讀一年Master移民］ 1年2.5萬非單程證大陸人湧港","createTime":"2019-04-25T12:33:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T03:41:32.000Z","uid":226548,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e8655d64d9b81fc8895d8e5d947b8942b1d89e76","tid":1125081,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T12:33:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/chinese-13_2eF4J_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fchinese-13_2eF4J_1200x0.png&h=3ff5dc6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據保安局向立法會財委會提供文件顯示，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">去年透過「優秀人才計劃」、「輸入內地人才計劃」等非單程證途徑申請來港而獲批的內地居民為 24,999 人</span></strong>，創下新高紀錄。其中透過「優秀人才計劃」獲批來港的有逾 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">9 成為內地居民</span></strong>，而內地居民申請「優才」獲批的成功率為 24%，遠高於非內地居民的獲批比率 4%。<br />\n<br />\n保安局早前向立法會財委會提交文件，根據議員陳志全的提問，詳列透過不同入境計劃（包括優秀人才入境計劃、輸入內地人才計劃、非本地畢業生留港／回港就業安排、科技人才入境計劃、資本投資者入境計劃）獲批來港及取得居留權的內地居民及非內地居民人數。<br />\n<br />\n2018 年透過<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「非本地畢業生留港／回港就業安排」</span></strong>獲派來港的 10,150 人，則有 9,206 人為內地居民，比率為 91%。過去五年，透過此政策留港的有 9 成均為內地居民。"},{"pid":"d27c415ffb4ec4415898af9449929f284811f184","tid":1125081,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T12:44:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a73cdc89d229357885a9a83215a5af5e6b6f191e","tid":1125081,"uid":224106,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T12:44:31.000Z","msg":"點會夠屋住<br />\n班賣港賊 落地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f55bb431e6f3a66342d2453ecd69b67c46c37e9d","tid":1125081,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T14:05:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f6988ba9a88690d589889448bb716d16c6033ab","tid":1125081,"uid":3818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T1